statements.sql: select * from information_schema.tables where table_schema = 'takeyourtrip' and table_name = 'script' and table_type = 'BASE TABLE'
select exists(select * from `banks` where `bank_name` = 'Abu Dhabi Commercial Bank') as `exists`
select column_name as `column_name` from information_schema.columns where table_schema = 'takeyourtrip' and table_name = 'banks'

insert into `banks` (`bank_name`, `currency_name`, `currency_code`, `currency_symbol`, `min_limit`, `max_limit`, `fixed_charge`, `percent_charge`, `rate`, `desc`, `image`, `slug`, `input_fields`, `updated_at`, `created_at`) values ('Abu Dhabi Commercial Bank', 'Dirham', 'AED', 'د.إ', '4', '1000', '2', '1', '3.67', '

Abu Dhabi Commercial Bank (ADCB) stands as a cornerstone of the banking sector in the United Arab Emirates (UAE), particularly in Abu Dhabi, the capital city. Established in 1985, ADCB has played a pivotal role in driving economic growth and financial stability in the region.

As one of the leading banks in the UAE, ADCB offers a comprehensive range of financial products and services to cater to the diverse needs of its customers. These services encompass retail banking, corporate banking, wealth management, and Islamic banking solutions, providing individuals, businesses, and government entities with tailored solutions to meet their financial objectives.

ADCB\'s commitment to innovation is evident through its adoption of cutting-edge technology and digital solutions to enhance customer experience. From online banking platforms to mobile applications, the bank ensures seamless access to banking services, empowering customers to manage their finances efficiently and conveniently.

', '094fa5e7-f3c1-4d2b-b325-f9428f18e33c.webp', 'abu-dhabi-commercial-bank', '[{\"type\":\"text\",\"label\":\"IBAN\",\"name\":\"iban\",\"required\":true,\"validation\":{\"max\":\"30\",\"mimes\":[],\"min\":\"1\",\"options\":[],\"required\":true}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"label\":\"Swift Code\",\"name\":\"swift_code\",\"required\":true,\"validation\":{\"max\":\"30\",\"mimes\":[],\"min\":\"1\",\"options\":[],\"required\":true}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"label\":\"full name in Emirates ID\",\"name\":\"full_name_in_emirates_id\",\"required\":true,\"validation\":{\"max\":\"30\",\"mimes\":[],\"min\":\"1\",\"options\":[],\"required\":true}}]', '2024-03-28 09:40:41', '2024-03-28 09:40:41')
